### Part 3: Redesign AI Terminal as Right Sidebar (4-6 hours)

**Current Architecture:**
```tsx
// AITerminal.tsx - Full-width overlay
<div className="fixed inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/2 ...">
  {/* Terminal content */}
</div>
```

**New Architecture:**
```tsx
// Right sidebar (mirrors left nav)
<div className={`
  fixed top-0 right-0 h-screen
  transition-transform duration-200
  ${isOpen ? 'translate-x-0' : 'translate-x-full'}
  w-[400px] lg:w-[500px]
  bg-black text-green-400  // Terminal-style colors
  border-l border-border-light dark:border-border-dark
  z-40
`}>
  {/* Terminal UI */}
</div>
```

**Design Specs:**

1. **Layout:**
   - Fixed right sidebar (400px mobile, 500px desktop)
   - Collapsible with toggle button (keep existing behavior)
   - Full height (0 to 100vh)
   - Slide in/out transition (translate-x)

2. **Terminal-Style UI:**
   - Black background (`bg-black`)
   - Green text (`text-green-400` for classic terminal look)
   - Monospace font (`font-mono`)
   - Terminal prompt style (`user@neuman-brain:~$`)
   - Command history (up/down arrows)
   - Clear screen command (`clear` or Cmd+K)

3. **Functionality:**
   - Keep existing AI provider selection
   - Keep existing conversation history
   - Keep existing message input
   - Add: Image generation support (if provider supports it)
   - Add: Code syntax highlighting
   - Add: Copy code button
   - Add: Terminal commands (clear, help, etc.)

**Files to Modify:**
1. `src/components/AITerminal.tsx` - Complete redesign
2. `src/App.tsx` or `src/components/Layout.tsx` - Adjust main content margin when open

**Image Generation Support:**
